name: Hedge Fund
description: Hedge Fund is a token that yields 20% rewards of Fook Token (AVAX). Fook Token pays holders 23% in USDC rewards, so by buying Hedge Fund, you will receive 20% of Fook + 23% in USDC rewards. Hedge Fund has a goal to take the rewards and invest in other projects, which will increase the value of Hedge Fund's Investment Portfolio, which will be used for buy backs of Hedge Fund.
